679
00:55:25,616 --> 00:55:27,660
<i>É o nosso lema</i>

680
00:55:27,994 --> 00:55:30,997
<i>Hakuna matata</i>

681
00:55:32,040 --> 00:55:34,876
<i>- Hakuna matata?
</i>-Isso, é o nosso lema.

682
00:55:35,209 --> 00:55:37,962
